Take the same amounts of ordinary oil and ground myrrh and mix them together. Then take a root of bryony and make an opening in the middle and put therein the above material. Cut a cover from the root that fits well and let it stay in the sunlight for one month continually and it will be made. Save it for your needs.

Oil to heal and ease every sore.

Take an amount of good turpentine and put in 1 handful of tamarind flowers and as much incense as you wish and let this stay to infuse for 2 whole days. Then distill it in a glass still on a slow fire and you will extract a most precious liquid with which you will treat all the above infirmities. Many persons have used it to rub aound sores and also this oil has been used to put in unguents instead of ordinary oil and it also removes the pain of every sore.

Very excellent oil for a cut or a wound.

